---
title: Carb Smart Jalapeño Popper Bunless Double Beef Burgers with Fresh Salad
description: Get all the fun of a jalapeño popper from a burger patty! This carb-smart meal features juicy, tender beef patties stuffed with a decadent filling of cream cheese, jalapeños and cheddar. Spring mix and toppings of red onions, tomatoes and spicy mayo balance out this meal.

Carb Smart (50 g carbohydrates or less) is based on a per serving calculation of the recipe's carbohydrate amount.

